dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Depths shown by soundings and bathymetric tints. Includes notes and sailing directions. At head of title: Harbor of refuge no. In upper margin: Harbor map no. "Verified by A.A. Humphreys, lt. topl. engrs. & ast." In lower margin: Final reduction for engraving by M.I. McClery, draughtsman. Topography engd. by O.A. Lawson, & lettering by J. Knight. Electrotyped by S. Siebert. Includes 2 coastal profiles: S.W. view of the entrance to Little Egg Harbor by the north or sod channel -- View of the entrance to Little Egg Harbor by the north channel.
